{"tid":456102,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[秒經] 跪求文書notebook推介","createTime":"2017-11-02T16:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T15:18:47.000Z","uid":68484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7ab072bd4cad49981d7f26d13546ef1a62665175","tid":456102,"uid":68484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:19:41.000Z","msg":"越黎越多功課 所以想買返部notebook拎出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係想輕便 同埋舊電用得耐 唔洗帶火牛出街<br />\n最好用落係順嘅 唔會lag機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時主要用黎做功課 文書野 睇下片 上網查資料咁<br />\n想要返window機 易上手d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會攞黎打機<br />\n剪片 畫圖都唔會<br />\nmon最好有13-15吋<br />\n電腦白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爬過少少文但睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇親d notebook都好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n筆直大約五六千 頂龍七千<br />\n窮學生冇乜錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知有冇巴絲有相關推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c7b937c842096407e520d68c08ac79ea199000","tid":456102,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:30:06.000Z","msg":"功課、文書野有幾複雜？<br />\n如果只係google doc打下字可能tablet/ipad就夠<br />\n呢個筆直買到既laptop 仲要win機又要輕可以周街去真係唔太易"},{"pid":"eb437c5ec34dee3e650ba3cc85cb0979a939c04b","tid":456102,"uid":18684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:34:33.000Z","msg":"文書買chromebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfed81bdb29f2a074ca97e714648a221887a4193","tid":456102,"uid":68484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:47:42.000Z","msg":"唔該哂上面兩位巴絲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我應該唔會考慮買ipad或者tablet了<br />\n最主要想要輕便同window機<br />\n續航力 mon果d都係bonus黎姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果筆直加到八九千會唔會多選擇d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c81976b8e1d1ab149d36e5f586cfb1a1dbfccf8","tid":456102,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.spools.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Gambol-G6807-notebook.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.spools.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2FGambol-G6807-notebook.jpg&h=fbe70776&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb2e4c729b5adc36f6388e8d11c790ae3193d188","tid":456102,"uid":123524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:38:06.000Z","msg":"二千有找<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www8.hp.com/hk/zh/campaigns/stream-family/overview.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww8.hp.com%2Fhk%2Fzh%2Fcampaigns%2Fstream-family%2Foverview.html&d=NcqQRCZ2A5PjWhcJ3PxkfkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c6495fec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www8.hp.com/hk/zh/campaigns/stream-family/overview.html</a>"},{"pid":"c6cc72df08481cd8f060c578c394852283032baf","tid":456102,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T22:29:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2002280b4bec292ec21005ceb55c7789567cbee","tid":456102,"uid":134665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:18:47.000Z","msg":"MacBook Pro 13inch without tb"}]}